product. Same effort. That's not a sales problem. It's a system problem.

3
00:00:08.246 --> 00:00:12.369
Your go-to-market is a chain. The weakest link sets the throughput. Push

4
00:00:12.369 --> 00:00:16.491
every link, you stay flat. Find the binding constraint, you grow. Most

5
00:00:16.491 --> 00:00:20.614
teams try ten things at once. The math says only one is

6
00:00:20.614 --> 00:00:23.706
