9
00:00:31.952 --> 00:00:35.388
logic, not AI guessing. Same answers, same result, every time.

10
00:00:35.388 --> 00:00:39.167
You leave with three numbers. Annual revenue leakage. Monthly cost of

11
00:00:39.167 --> 00:00:42.946
