14
00:00:49.818 --> 00:00:52.910
No CSV uploads. Your data stays where it is.

15
00:00:52.910 --> 00:00:57.033
From outside, three feeds run on autopilot. Your reviews — every champion

16
00:00:57.033 --> 00:01:01.156
