25
00:01:31.390 --> 00:01:34.482
Gates that must clear before the next phase unlocks.

26
00:01:34.482 --> 00:01:37.918
Go-to-market is physics, not vibes. Start the assessment. Your Intelligence

27
00:01:37.918 --> 00:01:41.010
Report is ready in one hour... See you soon!
